{
  "stem": "7282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one, [NON-ENGLISH]-- this I remember-- [NON-ENGLISH], he was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so when Russia took over Poland, and the border opened, so I, I start to have contact with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me that they have a brother, [NON-ENGLISH], he is still in the army, in the Russian Army during the war-- he was, what.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- we, we write to each other letters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave me their address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had-- I had contact with, with the older son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the point was, he was killed at the end of war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the, the other two brothers-- one [NON-ENGLISH], one Shejman-- [NON-ENGLISH] is now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Shejman, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess he was in Israel, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of-- and they had-- he had a daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Her name-- she is now in Israel, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she is in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had contact with her in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my father wasn't born in Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was born in Constantinople, in Russia, I guess, it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- and I, I don't know the whole story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During the war, they emigrated to Ostrog, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they-- he, he wasn't born in Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I do not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, I-- it wasn't any discussions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually at that time, it wasn't the discussions like we're having it now here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was altogether a bit different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What, everybody was busy to, to, to make a living if they could, what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They haven't got time for the kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, of course, we didn't have so many questions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, like, the father says, this is it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You haven't got any say on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
